        <p>ChangeDetection.com is a great way to monitor a website that you go to infrequently (in this example, once a year). They email you whenever a change happens</p>
<p>The link below is for google code jam&#39;s change log, and it is fun to see some of the minor copy tweaks the make over time.</p>
<h3>ChangeDetection - Change Log: Google Code Jam</h3>
<p><a href="http://www.changedetection.com/log/google/code/codejam_log.html">http://www.changedetection.com/log/google/code/codejam_log.html</a></p>

